Package edu.cmu.deiis.types

Class Summary
Annotation It is the super class for all the other subclasses that will be added into the system.
Annotation_Type It is the super class for all the other subclasses that will be added into the system.
GeneAnnotation In the gene level, two types of annotations exist, Gene True Answer Annotation and Tagged Gene Annotation.
GeneAnnotation_Type In the gene level, two types of annotations exist, Gene True Answer Annotation and Tagged Gene Annotation.
GeneTrueAnswerAnnotation In Gene True Answer Annotation, the gold standard answer was extracted from the provided file to generate “true answer” for our evaluable, which is a task-based standard to compare with the system output and give us the preliminary evaluation of the overall performance of the system.
GeneTrueAnswerAnnotation_Type In Gene True Answer Annotation, the gold standard answer was extracted from the provided file to generate “true answer” for our evaluable, which is a task-based standard to compare with the system output and give us the preliminary evaluation of the overall performance of the system.
SentenceAnnotation Basically, the system gets the input of a UIMA CAS, which is transformed from a text file given by the file path and name.
SentenceAnnotation_Type Basically, the system gets the input of a UIMA CAS, which is transformed from a text file given by the file path and name.
TaggedGeneAnnotation In Tagged Gene Annotation, the annotation extracted from the provided input file was compared with the golden standard answer to get the recall and precision based on textual similarity.
TaggedGeneAnnotation_Type In Tagged Gene Annotation, the annotation extracted from the provided input file was compared with the golden standard answer to get the recall and precision based on textual similarity.
